song_lyrics: He Pramukh Swāmī taṇu nām uchchāratā,
Shvāsmā vishvās, vibhuno dharatā... He Pramukh 1
Khamatā kaṣhṭa anek, bhakta kaṣhṭahartā... He Pramukh 2
Antare jīvanā, Harine maḍhatā... He Pramukh 3
‘Bhakti’ bhave vistārī, mukti arpatā... He Pramukh 4
title: He Pramukh Swāmī taṇu nām uchchāratā
